<td><a href="/wiki/File:Confederate_National_Flag_since_Mar_4_1865.svg" class="image" title="3rd National Flag"><img alt="3rd National Flag" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e2/Confederate_National_Flag_since_Mar_4_1865.svg/160px-Confederate_National_Flag_since_Mar_4_1865.svg.png" width="160" height="107" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></td>
