<li id="cite_note-76"><b><a href="#cite_ref-76" title="">^</a></b> Levine pg. 146-147</li>
<li id="cite_note-77"><b><a href="#cite_ref-77" title="">^</a></b> Eicher, <i>Civil War High Commands</i></li>
<li id="cite_note-78"><b><a href="#cite_ref-78" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talk:Confederate_States_of_America#flags" class="external free" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talk:Confederate_States_of_America#flags" rel="nofollow">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talk:Confederate_States_of_America#flags</a></li>
